<div id="introduction">

    <h3>Detecting and avoiding deception in human interaction </h3>

    <hr />

    <noscript>
        <div id="js-warning" style="background-color:orangered; padding:.5em;">
            <b style="color:whitesmoke;">
                Javascript is either not supported or is currently disabled in your browser. Please use another browser or enable Javascript, close and revisit this page to continue. If you continue to see this warning, please do not attempt to complete this study.
            </b>
        </div>
